data.description: Welcome to 864 Quaint Street! Located on a low traffic block in the Secane section of Ridley Township, this is an adorable two bedroom, one bathroom house. First floor features living room, dining room with hardwood floors, kitchen, mechanical closet and rear porch. In the second floor you’ll find two bedrooms and a 3 piece bathroom. Located within walking distance to the Septa Regional Rail. Features include new roof (2020), new HVAC (2018), new hot water heater (2023) and newer windows. Schedule your tour before it’s gone!
